OL,5, The BBC in India will separate in two  
OL,6, from Wednesday, as it seeks to meet the
OL,7, country's foreign investment rules.    
OL,9,FThe BBC will retain its newsgathering  
OL,10,Fteam in India for its English language 
OL,11,Fdigital, television and radio outlets  
OL,12,Fheadquartered in London.               
OL,14,FA new, independent, Indian-owned       
OL,15,Fcompany called the Collective Newsroom 
OL,16,Fwill now produce content for the BBC's 
OL,17,Fsix other Indian language services.    
OL,19,FThe move comes a year after BBC India's
OL,20,Foffices were searched by authorities.  
